89
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:45,701
Mr. Jiang.

90
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:48,232
You came to see Lele in person?

91
00:04:48,661 --> 00:04:49,060
Yeah.

92
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:50,760
Take a seat.

93
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,021
Sit.

94
00:04:52,981 --> 00:04:53,860
