113
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:29,500
But...

114
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:31,500
I may not

115
00:05:32,901 --> 00:05:35,141
be able to read it in a month.

116
00:05:46,781 --> 00:05:47,221
Lele.

117
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:50,620
