154
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:00,341
Hello.

155
00:07:01,981 --> 00:07:02,541
Quiet.

156
00:07:03,701 --> 00:07:04,781
I have an idea

157
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,221
