158
00:07:06,661 --> 00:07:07,420
A cardiac patient.

159
00:07:10,056 --> 00:07:10,820
Alright.

160
00:07:12,901 --> 00:07:13,704
I have to go.

161
00:07:13,901 --> 00:07:14,760
I'll walk you out.

162
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:15,581
See you.

163
00:07:15,781 --> 00:07:16,541
