168
00:07:38,701 --> 00:07:41,060
Yeah, we were working on Lele's case.

169
00:07:42,581 --> 00:07:43,740
I heard Su Ying

170
00:07:44,021 --> 00:07:44,981
got Jiang Dong here.

171
00:07:45,541 --> 00:07:46,620
Was Lele thrilled?

172
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:51,221
