180
00:08:08,936 --> 00:08:10,344
without eating properly?

181
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:11,300
Eat first.

182
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:13,101
Thank you, Yisen.

183
00:08:13,380 --> 00:08:14,581
No problem.

184
00:08:20,581 --> 00:08:21,060
Thirsty?

185
