284
00:14:20,701 --> 00:14:21,581
Don't underestimate me.

285
00:14:28,260 --> 00:14:30,248
Lele is willing to cooperate now.

286
00:14:30,900 --> 00:14:32,136
Her mom also told me

287
00:14:32,461 --> 00:14:33,421
